dcterms:description: A dataset for intrahepatic cholangiocarcinomas (IHCCs) subtype classification, collected from 168 patients with 332 whole slide images (WSIs). The dataset includes WSIs categorized into small duct type (SDT) and large duct type (LDT) based on gene mutation information.
dcterms:title: IHCCs subtype classification dataset

dcterms:description: A liver cancer dataset composed of 323 whole slide images (WSIs), which can be classified into hepatocellular carcinomas (HCCs) and intrahepatic cholangiocarcinomas (IHCCs). The dataset includes 121 WSIs for training and the remaining for testing.
dcterms:title: Liver cancer dataset
